Description:

Is there enough visibility into the impact that's being delivered? How can we improve it? And what if my manager is new?!

As with all livestreams, I'm looking forward to answering YOUR questions! So join me live and ask in the chat, or you can comment now and I can try to get it answered while I stream.

Title: Understanding Cursor Pagination and Why It's So Fast (Deep Dive)
Description: While offset pagination is widely used, cursor-based pagination offers significant performance advantages - my tests show a 17x speedup when paginating through a million-record dataset in PostgreSQL. Let's take a deep dive into cursor pagination, compare it with offset pagination, and examine the SQL execution plans.
